[[Category:Arabic nouns]]
===Etymology===
From the verb {{ARchar|[[قضب]]}} {{Unicode|(qáɖaba)}}, meaning 'to [[cut off]],' 'to [[prune]],' 'to [[trim]].' 

===Noun===
{{ARchar|قضيب}} {{Unicode|(qaɖí:b)}} {{m}}, {{ARchar|قضبان}} {{Unicode|(quɖbá:n)}} {{p}}

# [[branch]] or [[twig]] that has been cut off.
# [[stick]], [[rod]], [[wand]], [[staff]].
# [[penis]], [[phallus]].
#''(railroad)'' [[rail]].
#''(technical)'' [[guide rail]].

